      "bullets": [
        "Use semantic HTML <button> elements instead of <div> tags to inherit native keyboard focus and ARIA accessibility roles automatically.",
        "Ensure interactive elements support standard keyboard triggers like Space and Enter, matching native browser-level click behaviors.",
        "Prevent multi-click race conditions in asynchronous operations by managing state and disabling buttons without breaking screen reader focus."
      ]
